data.description: 4 bedrooms & 2.5 bath home in quiet neighborhood. Two-story foyer with tile floors that span into the kitchen. Great room sits right off of kitchen area-perfect for entertaining. Kitchen boasts breakfast room, breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances and plenty of cabinet space. Large master bedroom with trey ceilings and an extra-large walk in closet. Master bath has a double vanity, separate shower & garden tub. Fenced in back yard and an extended two car garage. Home is approx. 2300 sq. ft. Pool & playground Community.
